title: The Dennis Prager Show PODCAST SEP-27-2013 FRI
description:
The Dennis Prager Show PODCAST SEP-27-2013 FRI





Prager 20130927  3 Open Lines

Prager H3: Per usual, callers set the agenda.
 Issues raised include: should political and religious topics be excluded
 in a social situation;
 can you be conservative and not religious;
 is it okay to waste time.


Prager 20130927  2 Happiness Hour: Hanging with the Good

Prager H2: You will greatly increase your chances of happiness if
 you spend your time with good people.
 Choose your associates carefully, if you can.


Prager 20130927  1 QOL

Prager H1: The quality of life in this country has been overwhelmed by an obsession with safety.
 ''Better safe than sorry'' has superseded ''land of the free and home of brave.''

 What has the Cruz filibuster achieved?

 Is this an example of the Right engaging in Stage One thinking Are we being played by Iran?

 Again?
